Horst&#58; Since 3.3 is in critical/security bug-fix only mode (<a href='https&#58;//opensciencegrid.github.io/technology/policy/release-series/#life-cycle-dates' target='_blank' rel='nofollow'>https&#58;//opensciencegrid.github.io/technology/policy/release-series/#life-cycle-dates</a>), we won&#39;t backport a fix to 3.3. However, this is an easy configuration fix; you should be able to create /etc/tmpfiles.d/xrootd/ with the following contents&#58;

